```class Solution {
    public int addMinimum(String word) {
        int res = 0;
        int i = 0;
        while (i < word.length()) {
            if (i + 2 < word.length() && word.substring(i, i + 3).equals("abc")) {
                i += 3;
            } else {
                res += 3 - (word.length() - i) % 3;
                i = word.length();
            }
        }
        return res;
    }
}```
